---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Products"
  description="Selected digital health and AI products across endoscopy and radiology."
>
  <Section title="Products">
    <div class="list">
      <article class="item">
        <h3>Endoscopy Workflow Management</h3>
        <p>
          At Olympus, I work on endoscopy workflow management. The product work includes reporting,
          documentation, workflow automation, voice reporting, structured data capture, and
          interoperability with hospital systems.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>OLYSENSE / Intelligent Endoscopy</h3>
        <p>
          I have worked on product topics related to AI-enabled gastrointestinal endoscopy,
          including detection, diagnosis, and quality-related applications. This work is part of a
          broader shift from standalone AI algorithms toward connected endoscopy workflows.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI Endoscopy Products</h3>
        <p>
          My work has included product management for AI functionality in endoscopy use cases,
          aligned with medical software requirements and clinical workflow needs.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI-Rad Companion</h3>
        <p>
          At Siemens Healthineers, I worked on AI products for radiology image analysis, including
          regulated AI-based clinical applications.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <h3>AI-Rad Companion Chest X-ray</h3>
        <p>
          I worked on AI-Rad Companion Chest X-ray as a product management effort in X-ray
          diagnosis. The work involved radiology workflow, clinical evaluation, regulatory
          evidence, and product development.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
